# Tests Required

## Policy

No feature or bugfix merges without tests in the same change.

| Change type | Required tests |
|-------------|----------------|
| Schema / RLS | `supabase/tests/*.sql` |
| Package logic | Vitest `*.test.ts` |
| UI feature | Vitest + Testing Library; Playwright for journeys |
| Bugfix | Regression test named `regression_*` |
| Edge Function + SPA client | Vitest for client wrapper; RLS if migration adds RPC |

## Commands

- `pnpm test` — Vitest
- `pnpm test:rls` — Supabase RLS suite
- `pnpm test:e2e` — Playwright

Use skill: `.cursor/skills/edunudg-write-tests/SKILL.md`

Before finish: `.cursor/skills/edunudg-sync-artifacts/SKILL.md` (specs, docs, tests, skills, agents).

## Locators

- **Playwright**: `getByRole({ name })` is substring match — use `{ exact: true }` for shared prefixes (`Log in` vs `Log in with Google`).
- **Testing Library**: do **not** pass `exact: true` (not on `ByRoleOptions`; breaks typecheck). Use `exactAccessibleName("…")` from `@/test/exactAccessibleName` (anchored `/^…$/`).
- See `openspec/specs/staff-login/spec.md`.

